## Gemini space

New to Gemini? These are good jumping-off points:

=> gemini://geminiprotocol.net/ Project Gemini — the protocol itself
=> gemini://kennedy.gemi.dev/ Kennedy — search engine for gemini space
=> gemini://warmedal.se/~antenna/ Antenna — feed aggregator for gemlogs
=> gemini://bbs.geminispace.org/ BBS — geminispace forum

If you don't have a Gemini client yet, Lagrange is a beautiful one:

=> https://gmi.skyjake.fi/lagrange/ Lagrange
